{"tid":2310872,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息指中共軍機於今日中午時分靠近台灣北部領空","createTime":"2020-12-03T14:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T14:49:55.000Z","uid":292499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce254256e5bc4679ec1d6a127907bd2d32dd8d24","tid":2310872,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"12月03日  #中共軍機 出現北部空域，且接近我領空，我空軍在空警戒、並於11時02分、13時36分廣播驅離。<br />\n<br />\n本月累計進入我空域3天，連續第7天，本月廣播驅離紀錄共計07次。<br />\n<br />\n位置: 北部空域<br />\n<br />\n20201203_1102<br />\n抄件:中華民國空軍廣播，位於台灣北部空域高度3000公尺的中共軍機注意!你已進入我空域，影響我飛航安全，立即迴轉脫離!<br />\n20201203_1336<br />\n抄件:中華民國空軍廣播，位於台灣北部空域高度3000公尺的中共軍機注意!你已接近我領空，影響我飛航安全，立即迴轉脫離!<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/28IpzP0ykb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F28IpzP0ykb%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=6d5e86f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/28IpzP0ykb/</a>"},{"pid":"0fc43d495435e077b2812f95e9c33702147b729a","tid":2310872,"uid":221395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:38:39.000Z","msg":"又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d107dbe3e617f7f342922f6fd8d16840b31610b1","tid":2310872,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fc43d495435e077b2812f95e9c33702147b729a","tid":2310872,"uid":221395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:38:39.000Z","msg":"又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又"},{"pid":"976d1ffe4e7828c4bff06280dcc047717b9dca00","tid":2310872,"uid":349872,